.inner.container.client-entry(ng-if="client")
  h1.pageTitle {{client.first_name}}, reset your password to login.
  .row
    form.col-lg-12(name="clientForm")
      p Enter a new password:
      .client-input
        input.form-control(type="password" name="password" ng-model="client.password" validator="password")
        input.form-control(type="hidden" name="email" ng-model="client.email")
      .client-submit
        .btn.btn-primary.btn-login(ng-click="login()" validation-submit="clientForm" ng-disabled="clientForm.$invalid") Submit

.inner.container.client-entry(ng-if="!client")
  p(ng-if="!errMsg") One moment. If nothing happens in a few moments -
  p(ng-if="errMsg") {{errMsg}}
  a(ui-sref="login") Please click here to return to the login page.
